Shanghai Administrative Boundaries, Coast Lines and Islands, 2000 is a polyline theme representing administrative boundaries (country, provinces), coastlines, and islands in Shanghai Province in China for the year 2000. This data layer is part of the China 2000 Township Census data set produced by the All China Marketing Research Co. and distributed by the University of Michigan, China Data Center.
